data.description: Corner lot! No HOA! This 3 bedroom 2 bath single story home sits on the corner lot of well established neighborhood. Close to freeways and shopping. Room for RV. This charming home was recently painted inside and out. New AC and updated plumbing. Owned solar and wood burning fireplace. Large lot is a blank canvas to make your own!
